F. INSTALL Eclipse

G. Install Xampp, develope mengunakan browser.

H. COMPAILE 
   put data htdoct\folder to cordova folder project.


===== Open nodejs commnd from ==========

#new project ionic.
ionic start nmproject blank

#RUN BROWSER.
ionic serve.

#Compile:
ionic build android

#Configure Platforms
$ ionic platform add ios
$ ionic platform add android

#Just to make sure the default project worked, try building and running the project (substitute ios for android to build for Android instead):
$ ionic build ios
$ ionic emulate ios

#Plugin ionic
ionic plugin list

ionic plugin rm cordova-plugin-file

ionic plugin add cordova-plugin-file -- save

#Rebuild-path - Cached binary - import project
npm rebuild node-sass

